title: Miraculous Ladybug Episode 1-2 (Korean with Eng Subs) 720p
description:
720p, KOREAN WITH ENGLISH SUBS

Set in Modern-day Paris, the series focuses on teen high school girl Marinette Cheng, who is able to transform into the superhero, Ladybug.

Ladybbug has the superpower of luck and her side-kick Cat Noir has the power of bad luck. The duo protects Paris from the Akuma who are regular citizens transformed into villains.

CGI animated series, co-produced by Zagtoon, Method Animation, Toei Animation and SAMG Animation
